                            <comment id="13118837" author="cmenzel" created="Sat, 1 Oct 2011 15:46:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch against trunk contains:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;a test that demonstrates the wrong behavior of AutoLabelTextResolver&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;a fixed AutoLabelTextResolver that behaves correctly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;To fix the issue, I changed AutoLabelTextResolver to use a StringResourceModel when picking up a localized message via the key attribute. When it&apos;s using FormComponent#getDefaultLabel it now uses a LoadableDetachableModel to reliably pick up changes here. I also refactored the &quot;find the label content&quot; part of AutoLabelTextResolver#onComponentTag into a separate method to increase readability.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
